ed with prize money.\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many individual sports\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4465}, {\"ngram\": \"tournaments\", \"from\": 4476, \"to\": 4487}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4504}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 4516, \"to\": 4524}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4539}, {\"ngram\": \"prize money\", \"from\": 4558, \"to\": 4569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others have sponsorship agreements with sportswear brands and supplement companies, which can involve wearing branded apparel, appearing in advertisements, or promoting products on social media.\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Others\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4578}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsorship agreements\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4606}, {\"ngram\": \"sportswear brands\", \"from\": 4612, \"to\": 4629}, {\"ngram\": \"supplement companies\", \"from\": 4634, \"to\": 4654}, {\"ngram\": \"branded apparel\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4697}, {\"ngram\": \"advertisements\", \"from\": 4712, \"to\": 4726}, {\"ngram\": \"products\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4749}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Olympians can also receive assistance through the Australian Sports Commission'sdAIS athlete grant, which provides financial support to athletes for both the cost of living and sport-associated expenses.\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4768, \"end\": 4778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"score\": 0.8312510900866823, \"rank\": 0.19339761989619192, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Government\"}, {\"begin\": 4829, \"end\": 4857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \